onBytesReceived

protected void onBytesReceived(byte[] bytes)
(non-Javadoc) Receives bytes from Bluetooth device and sends them to the parser. Note that the received bytes by come in any length. The parser seeds to Frame the data and detect complete messages. When this happens the parser will call dataValueReceived with the complete message.

Specified by:
